lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"或者我真係唔知me too tag點解喇<br />\n<br />\n不過我係本身唔知點樣可以表示借人account<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔小心個topic有真係打少左字嘅<br />\n<br />\n 你啱<br />\n但我覺得呃like真係冇乜用囉<br />\n<br />\n因為佢實在太單方面啦<br />\n而且都解決唔到個根本問題<br />\n<br />\n今次係想盡量去用多角度<br />\n去睇問題嘅嚴重性<br />\n<br />\n你鍾意嘅都可以用大叔嘅角度同我講野呀<br />\n咁可以去方便分析個問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d58ea6fb4b1412932af2f854c3649703f5992f","tid":984283,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582ec7440425ab77ab13f868ddebf82b56d24a9e","tid":984283,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:54:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"sorry 打漏字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6084bea74607b27de5050b79b468ff9893394300","tid":984283,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21054a8f88214d7e9b95eb3c752096e39f9d4925","tid":984283,"uid":62011,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 篇野既格式係歌詞定現代詩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"sorry呀 唔太識打字<br />\n用語音輸入法<br />\n 所以先咁咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf0f36480655c8f4774ade75b23f4aa8d1b4c8d","tid":984283,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"邊一首歌"},{"pid":"3ee8988f645a1b04d3314710ddb2575b5eacc466","tid":984283,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582ec7440425ab77ab13f868ddebf82b56d24a9e","tid":984283,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:54:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"都有可能嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\